{
  "stem": "26728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'd all have cigarettes and maybe a bottle of brandy or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we'd sit in a circle and-- and he would answer questions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He'd been there for six or seven years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About the treatment, about the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The food, uh, in Buchenwald, near the end of the life of most of the camps, it was-- they didn't get any food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- Buchenwald was not the worst, but it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- there were unrecovered dead bodies all over the place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you go into a row-- between a row of barracks, andw what-- and there were dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to step over or around-- or around dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Usually they were naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what had happened, they were people that had died during the night, and the other inmates would just take them outside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had a detail of inmates whose job was to go to take these-- gather up these bodies, and put them in the stacks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Uh, and you know, like I say, the-- I don't know how to describe this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It just was surreal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To me, seeing, uh, a bunch of dead bodies, after a while, it didn't-- it didn't have any impact.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just was so terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I never felt like crying at Buchenwald, uh, except when I was in the one barracks where these people had-- had been.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were all dying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some of them were already dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But their fecal matter was just all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You walked in it this deep just to get inside the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And uh, And then you realized that these-- these-- they could look at you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
